548
00:32:04,750 --> 00:32:05,550
Well,

549
00:32:05,830 --> 00:32:07,150
she's just a bookworm,

550
00:32:07,390 --> 00:32:08,670
always off in her own world.

551
00:32:08,990 --> 00:32:10,580
