How have you been lately?

572
00:33:16,910 --> 00:33:18,060
Is everything alright?

573
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:19,610
Everything's good.

574
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:20,630
That's good.

575
00:33:21,390 --> 00:33:22,670
You're in the mortal realm

576
00:33:22,670 --> 00:33:23,790
all alone.

577
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,990
If anything happens,

578
00:33:25,070 --> 00:33:27,110
reach out to Mr. Loong or me.

579
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,790
Don't handle everything on your own.

580
00:33:29,230 --> 00:33:30,190
Okay.

581
00:33:30,230 --> 00:33:31,430
Thank you, Hannv.

582
00:33:31,670 --> 00:33:32,470
Oh, by the way,

583
00:33:32,870 --> 00:33:34,430
your birthday is coming up soon, isn't it?

584
00:33:36,270 --> 00:33:37,070
My birthday?

585
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:39,800
It's still a while away.

586
00:33:39,990 --> 00:33:41,500
I was born in the fall.

587
00:33:42,730 --> 00:33:44,050
I must have remembered it wrong.

588
00:33:44,630 --> 00:33:46,340
I want to make you an embroidery piece

589
00:33:46,370 --> 00:33:47,930
as a birthday gift.

590
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:49,910
I'll need your birth date and time for that.

591
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:52,310
Why don't you write them down for me?

592
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:53,670
Sure.

593
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:23,830
Kai Shan.

594
00:34:24,830 --> 00:34:26,389
Have you packed enough food for the trip?

595
00:34:28,179 --> 00:34:29,030
It's here.

596
00:34:31,730 --> 00:34:32,690
I'll go get her.

597
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:33,460
No need.

598
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:34,909
You two bring the food

599
00:34:34,909 --> 00:34:35,790
onto the carriage.

600
00:34:35,790 --> 00:34:36,670
I'll go get her.

601
00:34:46,590 --> 00:34:47,260
We're leaving.

602
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:56,270
Ji Tanyin.

603
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:02,190
When I heard you were back,

604
00:35:02,220 --> 00:35:03,620
I thought you were struck dead

605
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:04,760
by lightning again.

606
00:35:04,990 --> 00:35:05,800
No.

607
00:35:06,000 --> 00:35:07,200
Hannv called me,

608
00:35:07,270 --> 00:35:08,510
so I came back to check on things.

609
00:35:08,710 --> 00:35:09,760
With all gods in slumber

610
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:11,270
and you down in the mortal realm,

611
00:35:11,270 --> 00:35:13,570
the Heavenly Realm is eerily quiet!

612
00:35:14,020 --> 00:35:15,150
Isn't Hannv

613
00:35:15,150 --> 00:35:16,150
still here?

614
00:35:16,510 --> 00:35:17,750
She barely

615
00:35:17,750 --> 00:35:19,350
leaves the Luofu Sea.

616
00:35:19,350 --> 00:35:20,710
It doesn't make a difference if she's here or not.

617
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:21,510
Ji Tanyin.

618
00:35:22,470 --> 00:35:23,270
Ji Tanyin.

619
00:35:24,140 --> 00:35:24,950
Ji Tanyin.

620
00:35:25,310 --> 00:35:26,070
I'm not done talking.

621
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:26,790
I've got things to do.

622
00:35:26,790 --> 00:35:27,920
I'll come see you another day.

623
00:35:33,660 --> 00:35:34,460
How could she leave

624
00:35:35,030 --> 00:35:36,230
halfway through the conversation?

625
00:35:52,950 --> 00:35:53,750
You're awake.

626
00:35:56,780 --> 00:35:58,220
You didn't leave me behind this time.

627
00:35:58,790 --> 00:36:00,390
Our next stop

628
00:36:00,470 --> 00:36:01,750
is an amazing place.

629
00:36:02,300 --> 00:36:03,290
If you hadn't woken up,

630
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:05,590
I was gonna bury you there.

631
00:36:09,230 --> 00:36:10,550
What are you reading?

632
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:15,960
"The Story of the Mute Lady of Wu Mountain."

633
00:36:16,400 --> 00:36:17,280
Have you heard of it?

634
00:36:21,150 --> 00:36:22,710
It's said that the Mute Lady

635
00:36:22,990 --> 00:36:23,990
also once trained

636
00:36:23,990 --> 00:36:25,110
under your master, Xie You.

637
00:36:25,350 --> 00:36:27,550
And she was quite accomplished in craftsmanship.

638
00:36:27,990 --> 00:36:29,390
You and she studied under the same master.

639
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:31,350
Have you ever heard of her name?

640
00:36:32,230 --> 00:36:32,950
Back when Master

641
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:33,950
started taking students,

642
00:36:33,950 --> 00:36:35,310
he taught quite a few people.

643
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:37,700
I was focused on learning and didn't socialize much,

644
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:39,470
so I didn't get to know everyone.

645
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:48,600
What do you think of the book?

646
00:36:49,310 --> 00:36:50,500
It's quite interesting.

647
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,510
If everything in it is true,

648
00:36:52,590 --> 00:36:53,430
then this fellow disciple of mine

649
00:36:53,430 --> 00:36:54,780
is really impressive.

650
00:37:04,410 --> 00:37:07,710
[Orange Lake]

651
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:26,790
Madam, good morning.

652
00:37:43,410 --> 00:37:45,070
[Yunniang, a human]

653
00:37:45,750 --> 00:37:47,070
Mute Goddess of Wu Mountain,

654
00:37:47,070 --> 00:37:48,030
please bless me.

655
00:37:48,350 --> 00:37:49,190
May fortune fall from the sky

656
00:37:49,190 --> 00:37:50,030
while I sit at home.

657
00:37:50,030 --> 00:37:50,870
May rich fools come every day,

658
00:37:50,870 --> 00:37:51,630
generous with their money.

659
00:37:51,630 --> 00:37:52,500
May the poor stay away,

660
00:37:52,500 --> 00:37:53,750
and the ugly not make trouble.

661
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:57,790
Madam,

662
00:37:58,070 --> 00:37:59,200
you pray to the Mute Goddess every day

663
00:37:59,200 --> 00:38:00,070
for those things,

664
00:38:00,430 --> 00:38:01,830
but maybe taking San and me out

665
00:38:01,830 --> 00:38:03,470
to rob someone could fulfill your wishes faster.

666
00:38:04,390 --> 00:38:05,550
You think I wouldn't if I could?

667
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:08,160
Last night, I was thinking about it,

668
00:38:09,180 --> 00:38:10,880
and then I saw the Mute Goddess.

669
00:38:11,390 --> 00:38:12,470
No way.

670
00:38:14,510 --> 00:38:15,990
You've never seen her

671
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:17,480
for your prayers for wealth.

672
00:38:18,690 --> 00:38:19,690
It was in the backyard.

673
00:38:20,470 --> 00:38:21,830
The Mute Goddess chanted a passage

674
00:38:21,830 --> 00:38:23,270
of obscure scripture to me.

675
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:24,620
She also waved at me.

676
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:25,830
She had so many arms.

677
00:38:25,830 --> 00:38:26,950
It felt like she could snatch my soul

678
00:38:26,950 --> 00:38:27,870
at any moment.

679
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:30,390
I was so scared I couldn't sleep all night.

680
00:38:31,260 --> 00:38:32,910
The scripture the Mute Goddess chanted

681
00:38:32,910 --> 00:38:33,950
must've meant something important.

682
00:38:34,750 --> 00:38:35,990
How much do you remember?

683
00:38:37,910 --> 00:38:39,810
Her voice rose and fell,

684
00:38:40,350 --> 00:38:41,470
fading in and out.

685
00:38:42,340 --> 00:38:44,050
I even heard war drums in the background.

686
00:38:44,930 --> 00:38:46,050
I couldn't make out much.

687
00:38:46,350 --> 00:38:47,470
War drums?

688
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:50,630
Madam, did you drink last night?

689
00:38:52,860 --> 00:38:55,740
Was it at the west corner of the courtyard

690
00:38:55,830 --> 00:38:57,150
where you saw the Mute Goddess?

691
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:01,080
What? You saw her too?

692
00:39:02,730 --> 00:39:04,410
It was dark and foggy last night.

693
00:39:04,430 --> 00:39:06,390
Are you sure what you saw…

694
00:39:08,670 --> 00:39:09,430
wasn't that wild monkey

695
00:39:09,430 --> 00:39:10,230
that always sneaks in

696
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:11,510
to steal our food?

697
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:13,710
I was chopping meat until midnight last night.

698
00:39:13,730 --> 00:39:15,130
That weird chanting

699
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:16,190
with the sound of war drums

700
00:39:16,230 --> 00:39:17,790
could've been just the wind, right?

701
00:39:20,770 --> 00:39:22,060
Don't you have work to do in the kitchen?

702
00:39:22,310 --> 00:39:23,230
Are you trying to slack off again?

703
00:39:23,230 --> 00:39:24,510
Get out, get out!

704
00:39:30,640 --> 00:39:31,430
Madam,

705
00:39:31,470 --> 00:39:32,790
have some hot water.

706
00:39:34,190 --> 00:39:34,990
Madam,

707
00:39:35,230 --> 00:39:36,310
I've already

708
00:39:36,310 --> 00:39:37,390
flipped all the signs outside.

709
00:39:42,220 --> 00:39:43,860
Stop pretending to be diligent in front of me.

710
00:39:44,190 --> 00:39:45,140
Don't the chickens need to be fed?

711
00:39:45,430 --> 00:39:46,670
Doesn't the vegetable patch need watering?

712
00:39:46,670 --> 00:39:47,430
Get to work!

713
00:39:47,990 --> 00:39:49,070
I'm going right now.

714
00:40:05,390 --> 00:40:06,430
San, Si,

715
00:40:06,430 --> 00:40:07,230
why are we stopping?

716
00:40:07,430 --> 00:40:08,230
Madam,

717
00:40:08,460 --> 00:40:09,600
someone's blocking the way.

718
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:10,710
Where?

719
00:40:26,390 --> 00:40:27,190
Madam.

720
00:40:29,720 --> 00:40:31,110
That guy still hasn't woken up.

721
00:40:31,130 --> 00:40:32,070
The medicine from the physician

722
00:40:32,070 --> 00:40:33,070
isn't working.

723
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:40,110
What if he never wakes up?

724
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:41,740
Are we going to keep taking care of him like this?

725
00:40:41,820 --> 00:40:42,710
When his money runs out,

726
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:43,800
we'll throw him out.

727
00:40:46,790 --> 00:40:47,630
It's raining.

728
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:49,670
The vegetables in the yard!

729
00:40:49,690 --> 00:40:50,480
Go bring them in.

730
00:40:51,990 --> 00:40:52,790
Hurry!

731
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:02,930
Why didn't those two little beggars

732
00:41:03,250 --> 00:41:04,710
show up for food today?

733
00:41:35,540 --> 00:41:37,420
Is something wrong with your neck?

734
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:38,870
No.

735
00:41:39,390 --> 00:41:40,750
Then you were looking at me.

736
00:41:40,770 --> 00:41:41,580
I was not…

737
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:45,550
I'll take a rest.

738
00:41:45,790 --> 00:41:46,630
Don't disturb me.

739
00:42:00,950 --> 00:42:01,750
What's wrong with him?

740
00:42:03,530 --> 00:42:04,820
He said he wanted to take a nap.

741
00:42:05,020 --> 00:42:06,460
Where are we going now?

742
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,110
To Eastern Wilderness.

743
00:42:08,970 --> 00:42:09,770
Eastern Wilderness?

744
00:42:10,380 --> 00:42:11,990
What? You've been there before?

745
00:42:13,790 --> 00:42:14,430
But that was

746
00:42:14,430 --> 00:42:15,860
a long time ago.

747
00:42:16,030 --> 00:42:16,870
The most powerful

748
00:42:16,870 --> 00:42:17,990
weapon spirit among us

749
00:42:18,030 --> 00:42:19,180
is sealed there.

750
00:42:19,230 --> 00:42:20,190
Only Kai Shan thinks

751
00:42:20,190 --> 00:42:21,350
he's the most powerful.

752
00:42:21,350 --> 00:42:22,430
Don't take it seriously.

753
00:42:23,540 --> 00:42:25,150
Didn't you used to say the same thing?

754
00:42:25,230 --> 00:42:26,270
That was years ago.

755
00:42:26,390 --> 00:42:27,630
Things might be different now.

756
00:42:27,710 --> 00:42:28,440
I've improved a lot

757
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:29,630
over the years, after all.

758
00:42:29,910 --> 00:42:31,710
He was just more composed than me

759
00:42:31,710 --> 00:42:32,950
and more efficient in getting things done.

760
00:42:33,230 --> 00:42:34,430
What's his name?

761
00:42:35,350 --> 00:42:36,150
Lu Chen.

762
00:42:54,470 --> 00:42:55,750
What a godforsaken place.

763
00:42:56,190 --> 00:42:57,390
Being sealed here,

764
00:42:57,390 --> 00:42:58,630
Lu Chen must've had it tough.

765
00:43:01,710 --> 00:43:02,510
Someone's coming.

766
00:43:04,580 --> 00:43:05,500
Hello, sir.

767
00:43:05,540 --> 00:43:05,980
Hello.

768
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,960
Are you a local?

769
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:08,950
Yes.

770
00:43:09,070 --> 00:43:10,630
I'm from Rammed Earth City.

771
00:43:09,760 --> 00:43:10,690
[Bao, a human]

772
00:43:11,830 --> 00:43:13,350
We’re passing through

773
00:43:13,350 --> 00:43:14,230
and hoping to find a place

774
00:43:14,230 --> 00:43:15,270
to stay for the night.

775
00:43:15,430 --> 00:43:16,230
How far is it

776
00:43:16,230 --> 00:43:17,910
to Rammed Earth City from here?

777
00:43:19,030 --> 00:43:20,110
It's quite far.

778
00:43:20,150 --> 00:43:21,620
Go east for about seven miles

779
00:43:21,850 --> 00:43:23,730
and cross a bridge. Then you'll be there.

780
00:43:24,880 --> 00:43:25,870
Thank you.

781
00:43:30,030 --> 00:43:30,910
This old gentleman

782
00:43:30,910 --> 00:43:31,910
is in such good health.

783
00:43:31,910 --> 00:43:32,780
Not everyone at his age

784
00:43:32,780 --> 00:43:34,310
can carry such heavy stuff.

785
00:43:40,400 --> 00:43:41,340
It's getting dark.

786
00:43:41,340 --> 00:43:41,910
Shouldn't we

787
00:43:41,910 --> 00:43:43,190
find a place to stay for the night?

788
00:43:45,550 --> 00:43:46,710
There's a house up ahead.
